Firaministan Indiya zai halarci bikin bude wurin bautar a wani wuri da ake takaddama a kai
Firaministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin bude wani wurin ibada na mabiya addinin Hindu a wata unguwa da ake takaddama a kai a arewacin Indiya, inda masu tsattsauran ra'ayin addinin Hindu suka rushe wani masallaci na karni na 16 a shekarar 1992.
An shirya gudanar da bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, ranar da masu shirya bikin suka ce tana da alfanu ga mabiya addinin Hindu, amma kuma shekara guda kenan tun bayan da majalisar dokokin Indiya ta soke ikon cin gashin kai na jihar da Musulmi suka fi rinjaye, Jammu da Kashmir.
Wannan alama ce da ba za a iya watsi da ita ba ga magoya baya da masu adawa da jam'iyyar Bharatiya Janata Party ta Modi, ko BJP, wadda a shekarun da suka gabata ta yi alkawarin kwace ikon cin gashin kai na Kashmir da kuma gina wurin bauta ga gunkin Hindu Ram a inda masallacin Mughal ya taba zama, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh da masu ibada suka yi imanin cewa shi ne wurin haihuwar Ram.
Saboda cutar coronavirus har yanzu tana ci gaba da yaduwa a Indiya, wacce ta ba da rahoton mutum na uku mafi yawa a duniya, za a watsa bikin kai tsaye a gidan talabijin na kasar kuma za a iyakance adadin mahalarta da masu kallo, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kuma Kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, wata kungiyar mabiya addinin Hindu da ke kawance da BJP.
Mai magana da yawun kungiyar Vinod Bansal ya fada a wata sanarwa a ranar Asabar cewa, wurin ibadar zai zama "wata cibiyar zaman lafiya da hadin kan kasa da hadin kai da kuma farkawa da jin dadin Hindutva", ko kuma hanyar rayuwa ta Hindu.
An warware takaddamar da aka shafe tsawon karni ana yi kan filin a bara bayan nasarar da jam'iyyar BJP ta samu a zaben kasar.
A watan Nuwamba, Kotun Koli ta yanke hukunci a madadin haikalin, inda ta ce za a bai wa Musulmi fili mai fadin eka biyar a wani wuri na daban.
Mabiya addinin Hindu masu tsattsauran ra'ayi sun dade suna ikirarin cewa masu mamayar Mughal Musulmai ne suka gina masallaci a saman wani wurin ibada a tsohon birnin Ayodya.
A watan Disambar 1992 rikicin da ya biyo bayan lalata masallacin ya haifar da rikicin kabilanci inda aka kashe kimanin mutane 2,000, akasarinsu Musulmai.
A halin da ake ciki, ana ci gaba da sauraron karar da aka shigar a wata kotu ta musamman.
Wani masanin gine-gine daga garin Ahmedabad da ke jihar Gujarat, mahaifar Modi, ya gabatar da wani katafaren gini mai tsawon kafa 161 (mita 49) da ke dauke da dakuna biyar.
Yogi Adityanath, babban ministan Uttar Pradesh kuma mabiyin addinin Hindu, ya bukaci Ayodhya ta gudanar da bikin tsaftacewa da tsarkakewa na musamman da kuma dukkanin wuraren ibada na birnin don kunna fitilun mai a gaban ziyarar Modi, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Press Trust of India.
Adityanath ya ce bikin ya kawo karshen gwagwarmayar da aka kwashe shekaru 500 ana yi, in ji PTI.
