An cinna wa ginin kotu wuta a lokacin zanga-zanga a California
'Yan sanda a Oakland da ke California sun ce masu zanga-zanga a California sun cinna wa wani ginin kotu wuta, suka lalata wani ofishin 'yan sanda, sannan suka yi awon gaba da wasu jami'ai bayan da zanga-zangar lumana ta kara kamari a yammacin ranar Asabar.
Ma'aikatar Oakland ta wallafa a shafinta na Twitter cewa masu zanga-zangar sun farfasa tagogi, sun yi zane-zane, sun harba tartsatsin wuta da kuma harba lasisi a kan jami'an tsaro.
Da dama tweets kira ga zaman lafiya da kuma tambayi shirya don "taimaka mana samar da hadari sarari da kuma hadari wurare domin masu zanga-zanga".
Zanga-zangar ta fara ne da yammacin ranar Asabar tare da kungiyoyi irin su "Wall of Moms", kwatankwacin wata kungiya da ta kafa a Portland, Oregon, yayin da masu zanga-zangar suka fuskanci jami'an Amurka da aka tura zuwa wannan birni don tsare ginin kotun tarayya.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya domin su murkushe zanga-zangar da ake yi duk dare tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
Zanga-zangar a Oakland ta fara ne cikin lumana, amma daga bisani ta rikide ta koma tashin hankali.
'Yan sanda sun ayyana taron a matsayin wanda ya saba doka da misalin karfe 11:30 na dare, inda suka bukaci jama'a da su fice.
Wata kafar yada labarai ta bayar da rahoton cewa gobarar ta tashi ne a harabar kotun da ke Alameda County, kuma an shawo kanta bayan wani dan lokaci.
'Yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zangar a wani lokaci "sun farfasa tagogi tare da rera wakokin nuna wariyar launin fata ga mazauna wurin".
Hotunan da sashen ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter sun nuna yadda aka fasa gilasai da fenti a wani ginin 'yan sanda.
An tsaurara matakan tsaro a kofar ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke Chengdu, China
An tsaurara matakan tsaro a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke birnin Chengdu na kasar China a ranar Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurka ke shirin ficewa daga ofishin.
An ga manyan motoci uku suna shiga harabar ginin, yayin da 'yan sanda sanye da kayan soja da na farar hula suka yi layi a bangarorin biyu na titin, wadanda ke da shinge na karfe.
Editan jaridar Global Times ta China ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa an bai wa ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke Chengdu wa'adin sa'o'i 72 ya rufe, ko kuma zuwa karfe 10 na safiyar Litinin, 27 ga watan Yuli.
Kasar Sin ta yi zargin cewa wasu ma'aikata a karamin ofishin jakadancin Chengdu suna gudanar da ayyukan da ba su dace da halayensu ba.
Ba tare da yin cikakken bayani ba, mai magana da yawun ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin Wang Wenbin ya ce, irin wannan aiki ya yi katsalandan cikin harkokin kasar Sin kuma ya cutar da muradunta na tsaro.
An bayar da umarnin rufe ofishin jakadancin China da ke Chengdu ne a ranar Juma'a a matsayin ramuwar gayya kan umarnin da Amurka ta bayar na rufe ofishin jakadancin China da ke Houston, jihar Texas.
Washington ta umarci China ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare ikon mallakar fasaha na Amurka da kuma bayanan sirri na Amurkawa".
Yayin da rufe ofishin jakadancin China a Houston ya fara aiki a ranar Juma'a, an ga wasu mutane da suka yi kama da jami'an Amurka sun kutsa kai cikin ofishin ta kofar baya.
Wang ya fada a ranar Asabar cewa hakan ya saba wa yarjejeniyoyin kasa da kasa da na kasashen biyu, kuma China za ta mayar da martani, ba tare da bayyana yadda za ta mayar da martani ba.
Rufe iyakokin ya kara rura wutar rikicin da ke tsakanin kasashen biyu kan batutuwa da suka hada da cinikayya da leken asirin masana'antu da kuma kare hakkin dan adam.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce akwai dubban masu tayar da kayar baya a Afghanistan
Wani rahoton Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ce sama da 'yan tawayen Pakistan 6,000 ne ke boye a Afghanistan, kuma yawancinsu 'yan kungiyar Taliban ne da aka haramta, wadanda ke da alhakin kai hare-hare a kan sojoji da fararen hula a Pakistan.
Rahoton da aka fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar da aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta hade da wani bangare na kungiyar IS da ke Afghanistan.
Wasu daga cikin mambobin kungiyar TTP ma sun shiga kungiyar IS, wacce ke da hedikwata a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta amsa tambayoyin da kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya yi mata ba a ranar Lahadi.
Rahoton ya ce kungiyar IS a Afghanistan, wadda aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, ta sha fama da hare-hare daga jami'an tsaron Afghanistan da kuma dakarun Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wasu lokutan daga kungiyar Taliban ta Afghanistan.
Kwamitin bincike da sanya ido kan takunkumi na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ne ya shirya rahoton, wanda ke bin diddigin kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda a fadin duniya.
Rahoton ya yi kiyasin cewa mambobin kungiyar IS a Afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma yayin da shugabancinta ya ragu, har yanzu kungiyar IS na da wani dan kasar Syria mai suna Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani a cikin shugabanninta.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar masu sa ido sun samu labarin cewa wasu manyan kwamandojin kungiyar IS biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, sun isa Afghanistan kwanan nan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya.
"Duk da cewa kungiyar IS ta ja da baya, har yanzu tana da karfin kai munanan hare-hare a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Har ila yau, yana nufin jawo hankalin mayakan Taliban da ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da Amurka, "in ji rahoton, yana nufin yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya da Amurka ta sanya hannu tare da Taliban a watan Fabrairu.
An cimma wannan yarjejeniyar ne don bai wa Amurka damar kawo karshen katsalandan din da ta yi a Afghanistan na tsawon shekaru 19, tare da yin kira ga kungiyar Taliban da ta tabbatar da cewa kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda ba za su yi amfani da yankin ba.
Ana kuma sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta tabbatar da cewa Taliban za ta shiga cikin yakin da ake yi da IS.
Bangare na biyu kuma mai yiwuwa mafi muhimmanci na yarjejeniyar ya bukaci tattaunawa tsakanin Taliban da shugabannin siyasar Kabul.
A yammacin ranar Asabar, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka ta fitar da wata sanarwa da ke cewa wakilinta na wanzar da zaman lafiya Zalmay Khalilzad na ci gaba da zirga-zirga a yankin da nufin fara tattaunawar, wadda aka dakatar da ita akai-akai yayin da bangarorin biyu ke takaddama kan shirin sakin fursunoni.
Yarjejeniyar da Amurka ke goyon baya ta bukaci gwamnatin Afghanistan ta saki fursunonin Taliban 5,000, ita kuma Taliban ta saki jami'an gwamnati da sojoji 1,000 a matsayin wani mataki na nuna kyakkyawar niyya gabanin tattaunawar.
Har ya zuwa yanzu gwamnati ta ki sakin fursunonin Taliban kusan 600 da ta kira manyan masu laifi kuma ta ba da damar sakin wasu.
Taliban dai ta ki amincewa da hakan.
Wata sanarwa da ma'aikatar harkokin wajen Amurka ta fitar, ta ce bangarorin sun fi kusa da fara tattaunawar cikin gida a Afghanistan, mataki na gaba da zai kawo karshen yakin da aka kwashe shekaru 40 ana yi a Afghanistan.
"Ko da yake an samu gagarumin ci gaba game da musayar fursunoni, amma batun na bukatar karin kokari don warware shi gaba daya".
Mai magana da yawun kungiyar Taliban a siyasance a farkon makon nan ya ce a shirye kungiyar take ta tattauna da shugabannin siyasar Kabul bayan bikin babbar sallah da za a yi a karshen watan nan, idan an kammala sakin fursunonin.
Wani babban abin damuwa ga Pakistan shi ne kasancewar mayaka a Afghanistan, musamman wadanda ke da alaka da kungiyar TTP ko Jamaat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda ke da alaka da kungiyar Baluchistan Liberation Army, wadda ta dauki alhakin hare-haren da aka kai a wannan watan a kudancin lardin Sindh da kuma kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan.
An kashe sojojin Pakistan da dama a wannan watan a lardin Baluchistan da ke kudu maso yammacin kasar a wani fada da suka yi da masu tayar da kayar baya.
Kungiyar TTP ta dauki alhakin daya daga cikin hare-hare mafi muni da aka kai a Pakistan a shekarar 2014, lokacin da aka kai hari kan wata makarantar sojojin Pakistan, inda aka kashe mutum 140.
Mafi yawansu dalibai ne, kuma wasu ba su wuce shekara 5 ba.
Rahoton ya ce: "Yawan mayakan 'yan ta'adda 'yan asalin Pakistan da ke Afghanistan, wadanda ke barazana ga kasashen biyu, ya kai tsakanin 6,000 zuwa 6,500, kuma mafi yawansu 'yan kungiyar TTP ne".
Babban bankin Birtaniya HSBC ya musanta cewa "ya kafa tarko" ga kamfanin Huawei na China a binciken da Amurka ke yi - china radio international
Bankin HSBC mai hedikwata a London ya wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta cewa ba kamar yadda kafofin watsa labaran China suka yi ikirari ba ne, "ana kirkirar hujjoji" a kan kamfanin Huawei, abin da ya kai ga kama babban jami'in kudi na kamfanin a Canada.
A wani sako da aka wallafa a shafin sada zumunta na WeChat, bankin ya ce matakin da ya dauka bai haifar da binciken da Amurka ke yi wa kamfanin ba, wanda shi ne mafi girma a duniya wajen samar da kayayyakin sadarwa, saboda binciken da ake yi wa Huawei kan zargin karya takunkumin da Amurka ta kakaba wa Iran ya fara ne tun kafin bankin ya shiga cikin lamarin a karshen shekarar 2016.
"HSBC ba ta da wata kiyayya ga Huawei kuma ba ta "kama" Huawei ba", in ji bankin a ranar Asabar, inda ta kara da cewa ba za ta taba karkatar da duk wani bayani game da abokan cinikinta ba.
"Da yake amsa tambayoyin ma'aikatar shari'a ta Amurka, HSBC Group kawai ya gabatar da gaskiyar gaskiya.
HSBC ba ta "ƙirƙira" shaida ko "ɓoye" gaskiya ba. "
Har ila yau, a kan rt.com Matakin Birtaniya na dakatar da Huawei daga cibiyar sadarwa ta 5G ya nuna Amurka ta tsara manufofin kasashen waje na Birtaniya - George Galloway zuwa Boom Bust
The post da aka katange a kan dandamali tare da wani bayanin kula da cewa shi "karya dokokin" kuma ba samuwa a yanzu.
Sanarwar ta zo ne jim kadan bayan da kafafen yada labarai da dama na China, ciki har da jaridun da ke da alaka da gwamnati, suka zargi HSBC da hada baki da Washington don kafa tarko ga kamfanin Huawei.
Kamfanin ya kasance a tsakiyar rikicin diflomasiyya sama da shekara daya da rabi tun lokacin da aka kama babban jami'in kamfanin Huawei Meng Wanzhou a watan Disambar 2018 a Canada bisa sammacin da Amurka ta bayar.
Meng na fuskantar tuhumar zamba bisa zargin amfani da wani kamfani don karya takunkumin da aka kakaba wa Iran da kuma zargin yin karya ga bankuna game da alakar da ke tsakanin Huawei da kamfanin Skycom na Iran.
A cewar wata sabuwar shaida da jaridar Global Times ta wallafa, HSBC na da masaniya game da alakar kamfanin na China da Skycom.
Rahotanni sun ce bankin ya zabi ya hada kai da gwamnatin Amurka don kauce wa hukunci mai tsanani a shekarar 2012, lokacin da bankin ya amince da halasta kudaden haram da kuma karya takunkumi, ciki har da takunkumin da aka kakaba wa Iran.
An umarce shi a lokacin da ya biya kusan dala biliyan 1.9 a cikin takunkumi da kuma hana duk wani kuskure mai kama da haka.
"Hujjojin sun nuna cewa HSBC ya fahimci wannan dangantaka amma da gangan ya sayar da takardun sirri na kasuwancin abokin cinikinsa ga bangaren Amurka don gwamnatin Amurka ta iya watsi da kuskuren bankin Birtaniya kuma ba za ta hukunta shi ba a karkashin yarjejeniyar 2012 Deferred Prosecution Agreement", in ji jaridar a daya daga cikin labaran da ta rubuta a kan batun.
A cikin gargadi mai ban tsoro, jaridar da ke kula da Beijing ta kara da cewa mai ba da bashi, idan an tabbatar da laifin wannan "collusion", zai iya fuskantar "hukunci mai tsanani" a kasar Sin, daya daga cikin manyan kasuwanni na HSBC.
Ba wannan ne karo na farko da babban bankin ya fuskanci suka ba a cikin 'yan makonnin nan.
A watan da ya gabata, an caccaki HSBC saboda goyon bayan sabuwar dokar tsaron kasa ga Hong Kong, birnin da kasuwancinta ya fara kuma wanda ke samar da fiye da rabin ribar da take samu.
Bankin ya fuskanci suka daga bangarorin biyu - daga kasashen yammaci, inda Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya kira goyon bayan a matsayin "cin mutuncin kamfanoni", da kuma gabas, inda rahotanni suka ce bangaren China ya ce goyon bayansa ya "bata lokaci".
Jami'an kashe gobara sun yi nasarar kashe gobarar da ta tashi a Lassen County
Masu kashe gobara suna samun nasara a kan gobarar daji guda biyu da suka kone fiye da eka 30,000 a yankin Lassen da ke arewa maso gabashin Sacramento.
The Gold wuta, wanda ya fara kudu da Adin, ne 40% dauke kamar yadda ya ci gaba da barazana ga gidaje da kuma ranches kazalika da aikin noma, dabbobi da kuma katako ayyukan, Cal wuta jami'an ce a cikin wani update Asabar da safe.
Bayan ta shafe kwanaki hudu tana ci, wutar ta mamaye eka 21,000, ta lalata gidaje bakwai, ta kuma tura jami'an kashe gobara biyu zuwa asibiti.
A cikin dare, masu kashe gobara sun yi amfani da yanayin da ya fi dacewa don gina da kuma ƙarfafa layin sarrafawa.
Amma ana sa ran iska mai karfi da rashin iska mai yawa a ranar Asabar.
A yammacin Susanville, wata karamar gobara da aka fi sani da Hog fire ta lalata gine-gine biyu kuma ta cinye kusan eka 10,000.
A cewar ma'aikatar kula da gandun daji da kare gobara ta California, wutar ta kwanta a cikin dare yayin da ma'aikatan kashe gobara suka yi aiki don share da kuma karfafa layin sarrafawa.
Da safiyar ranar Asabar, kashi 45 cikin dari na wutar sun kare, kuma sun shafe kwanaki shida suna ci.
A cikin rana zafi, tare da yanayin zafi sama da 90 digiri a cikin Susanville yankin, smoldering faci kasance a hadarin flaring up.
Yayin da ake barin wasu mazauna su koma gidajensu, wasu yankunan da ke yankunan biyu na ci gaba da kasancewa a karkashin umarnin kwashe mutane.
An sallami ma'aikatan kashe gobara biyu da suka ji rauni a gobarar ta Gold daga asibiti.
Aljeriya: Mutuwar Mahmoud Guemama - Aljeriya ta rasa dan kishin kasa, mai sadaukar da kai, in ji Shugaba Tebboune.
Shugaban kasar Aljeriya, Abdelmadjid Tebboune, ya aike da sakon ta'aziyya ga mambobin majalisar wakilan jama'ar kasar (APN), Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wanda ya mutu a ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce Aljeriya "ta yi rashin dan kishin kasa kuma dan gwagwarmaya da ya sadaukar da kansa ga al'ummarsa da kuma al'ummarsa".
Aljeriya ta yi rashin nasara a yau, sakamakon mutuwar Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, dan kishin kasa kuma dan gwagwarmaya da ya sadaukar da kansa ga al'ummarsa da kuma al'ummarsa, mutumin da bai taba yin watsi da kudurinsa ba tun daga lokacin da ya dauki makamai, tare da 'yan uwansa masu jihadi, har zuwa numfashinsa na karshe a wannan ranar bakin ciki lokacin da za mu iya mika kanmu ga nufin Allah, "in ji Shugaba Tebboune a cikin sakon ta'aziyyarsa.
Shugaban kasar ya kara da cewa: "Marigayi Mahmoud Guemama, tsira da amincin Allah su tabbata a gare shi, ya kasance daya daga cikin fitattun 'yan gwagwarmaya masu kishin kasa wadanda suka sadaukar da kansu ga kasarsu".
"Marigayin ya sadaukar da rayuwarsa don 'yantar da Aljeriya daga azabar mulkin mallaka, ta hanyar shiga cikin rundunar juyin juya halin a cikin shekarun 1960 a sansanin horo na Tahart na tarihi na VI".
Shugaba Tebboune ya ce: "Kowa ya san marigayin saboda irin gwagwarmayar da ya nuna da kuma jajircewarsa wajen tabbatar da kasar Aljeriya mai wadata da hadin kai".
"A yankin kudu mai nisa, marigayi Mahmoud Guemama ya shahara sosai a matsayin mai shiga tsakani, yana shiga tsakani don sulhunta 'yan'uwa a cikin kasa guda a duk lokacin da aka kunna wutar sabani", in ji shugaban a cikin sakon nasa.
"Duk wadannan halaye da dabi'u sun sa marigayi Mahmoud Guemama ya samu girmamawa da amincewar al'ummar Tamanrasset wadanda suka zabe shi ya wakilce su a majalisar wakilan jama'ar kasar (APN) na tsawon wa'adi da dama, a lokacin da ya kasance jakadan da kuma mai kare damuwar yankin da kuma burin jama'arsa, har ma da wakilin da kuma mai magana da yawun dukkan 'yan Algeria", in ji shugaban kasar.
""Duk maganganun ta'aziyya ba za su isa ba don ba da ladabi ga mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, zaman lafiya ya tabbata a gare shi.
Ya bar mu ne a yau a daidai lokacin da Aljeriya ke bukatarsa", in ji shugaban kasar.
"Ina rokon Allah Madaukakin Sarki da ya kewaye marigayin da rahamarsa mai tsarki, ya karbe shi a cikin aljanna mai girma tare da shuhadaa da salihan bayi.
Ina kuma rokon Allah ya ba iyalansa da masoyansa hakuri da kwanciyar hankali...babu wani karfi ko iko sai da Allah", in ji shugaban kasar.
Zanga-zanga a Seattle: Wuta da barkonon tsohuwa yayin da dubban mutane suka yi tattaki a birnin
SEATTLE - Bayan makonni na rikice-rikice tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Ore., wani taron mutane kimanin 2,000 ya tattara a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna tafiya a kan tituna kuma sun yi arangama da 'yan sanda.
'Yan sanda uku sun ji rauni, ciki har da wanda aka kwantar a asibiti sakamakon raunin da ya samu a kafarsa sakamakon fashewar wani abu, sannan an kama masu zanga-zanga 16 da yammacin jiya, a cewar 'yan sanda.
Masu zanga-zangar dauke da rubuce-rubuce irin su "Feds Go Home" da kuma ihun "Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya", masu zanga-zangar sun tsaya a wurin da za a gina wata cibiyar tsare matasa sannan suka cinna wa gine-ginen wuta.
Wasu sun fasa tagogin shagunan da ke kusa da wurin.
'Yan sanda sun fuskanci taron jama'a a unguwar Capitol Hill, inda suka yi amfani da gurneti da barkonon tsohuwa kafin su fara kama mutane.
Bipasha Mukherjee, mai shekaru 52, daga Kirkland, Washington, ta ce tana zanga-zanga a kan tituna tun watan Mayu kuma ta ce abin damuwa ne a gare ta ganin irin wannan dabarun da 'yan sanda ke amfani da su.
"Wannan ba ita ce kasar da na yi hijira zuwa ba", in ji Ms. Mukherjee, wacce ta zo daga Indiya sama da shekara 30 da suka gabata.
"Yana jin kamar muna saurin zama mulkin kama karya da kuma mulkin 'yan sanda".
Michaud Savage na Seattle ya ce zanga-zangar ta shafi kananan hukumomi ne da kuma jami'an gwamnatin tarayya wadanda suka murkushe zanga-zangar da aka kwashe tsawon lokaci ana yi a Portland.
Mr. Savage ya ce dabarun da jami'an tsaro ke amfani da su a Portland, wadanda suka hada da amfani da hayaki mai sa hawaye da kuma bindigogi masu sarrafa kansu, suna da hadari kuma ba su dace ba.
"Yana da matukar wuya slide a cikin wani musamman tashin hankali shugabanci", Mr. Savage ce kamar yadda ya wanke idanunsa na barkono SPRAY da kuma reno a rauni a kan hannu daga wani walƙiya gurneti.
Mutuwar George Floyd a hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a watan Mayu ya haifar da zanga-zangar da ta jawo miliyoyin mutane suka fito kan tituna a birane da dama, amma zanga-zangar ta ragu a yawancin birane.
Seattle da Portland, duk da haka, sun ga zanga-zanga mai tsawo.
Masu zanga-zanga a Seattle sun yi ikirarin mallakar bangarori da dama na unguwar Capitol Hill inda suka ayyana yankin a matsayin mai cin gashin kansa.
Bayan da jerin harbe-harben da aka yi a wurin ya sa 'yan sanda suka share wurin, sai zanga-zangar ta lafa.
Portland, a halin yanzu, ya ci gaba da zanga-zanga, tare da wasu daga cikin manyan zanga-zangar a kusa da gine-ginen gwamnatin tarayya a birnin.
Bayan da Shugaba Trump ya bayar da umarnin kare mutum-mutumi da dukiyar gwamnatin tarayya, Ma'aikatar Tsaron Cikin Gida ta tura jami'an tsaro zuwa birnin, lamarin da ya haifar da jerin rikice-rikicen da suka haddasa jikkatar masu zanga-zanga, binciken sufeto janar da kuma kiraye-kirayen da shugabannin yankin suka yi ga jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da su fice.
Dubban mutane ne suka yi zanga-zanga a birnin, kuma ana ci gaba da gudanar da zanga-zanga.
A wannan makon, jami'an gwamnatin tarayya sun tura wata tawaga zuwa Seattle, kuma masu zanga-zangar sun bayyana hakan a matsayin dalilin da ya sa suka yi zanga-zangar a ranar Asabar.
Yayin da zanga-zangar Portland ta mayar da hankali a cikin gari, zanga-zangar ta ranar Asabar ta mamaye yankunan gabashin tsakiyar gari, inda ginin kotun tarayya na birnin yake.
