A halin yanzu 'yan sanda na gudanar da bincike kan wasu jerin kalaman batanci da aka wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta na mawakin na Grime.
Sakatariyar harkokin cikin gida ta wallafa a shafinta na Twitter a ranar Lahadi cewa: "Zargin nuna wariyar launin fata da Wiley ya yi abin kyama ne".
"Bai kamata su ci gaba da kasancewa a shafin Twitter da Instagram ba na tsawon lokaci kuma na bukace su da su yi cikakken bayani".
"Ya kamata kamfanonin sada zumunta su gaggauta cire irin wannan kiyayya daga shafukan su".
An zargi Twitter da "yin watsi da wariyar launin fata" saboda har yanzu ana iya ganin sakonnin da Wiley ya wallafa sa'o'i 12 bayan an fara wallafa su.
Tuni dai aka cire wasu daga cikin sakonnin da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter, kuma shafin ya dakatar da shi tsawon kwana bakwai.
Twitter a baya ya ce an kulle asusun Wiley na wucin gadi "saboda karya dokokinmu na nuna kiyayya", yayin da Facebook ya ce "babu inda za a yi kalaman kiyayya a Instagram".
Rundunar 'yan sanda ta birnin London ta fada a ranar Asabar cewa: "Hukumar 'yan sanda tana daukar duk wani rahoto na nuna wariyar launin fata da matukar muhimmanci.
A halin da ake ciki, kamfanin sarrafa Wiley, A-List Management, ya yanke duk wata alaka da tauraron.
Tsohon manajan mawakin, John Woolf, wanda Bayahude ne, ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "Biyo bayan kalaman batanci da Wiley ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter a yau, mu a @A_ListMGMT mun yanke duk wata alaka da shi.
Tun da farko ya ce bai goyi bayan ko ya amince da abin da Wiley ya wallafa ba amma zai yi magana da shi cikin sirri kuma ya "taimaka masa wajen ilmantar da shi".
Sai dai a wani bidiyo da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Instagram, Wiley ya ce shi ne ya yanke alakar da ke tsakaninsa da masu kula da shi.
Sauran 'yan majalisar sun soki Twitter saboda barin sakonnin su ci gaba da kasancewa a bayyane.
Dan majalisar wakilai na jam'iyyar Labour Jess Phillips ya fada a ranar Asabar cewa:
"Kawai ganin dukan Wiley kaya. Me ya sa a cikin ƙasa sun @Twitter bar up irin wannan blatant nuna wariyar launin fata da kuma ƙiyayya? Yana hits dukan m beats, Yahudawa samun abubuwan da ba ka samu, su ne a cikin iko, suka yi zaton su fi... Wannan shi ne m kaya. Lalle ne ya kamata ya sauko. "
Fellow MP Neil Coyle kara da cewa: "Ya management bayyana iya aiki da sauri fiye da @Twitter jaddada, sake, cewa dokokin (ciki har da Online Harms Bill) ya kamata a tabbatar da kafofin watsa labarun dandamali ba a yi amfani da su yada kiyayya".
John Mann, mai bai wa gwamnati shawara kan batun kyamar Yahudawa, ya ce sakonnin da aka wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta "sun nuna dalilin da ya sa ya kamata a sauya doka ta yadda za a yi musu adalci".
A halin da ake ciki, kungiyar Campaign Against Antisemitism ta bukaci 'yan sanda da su gudanar da bincike kan abubuwan da Wiley ya wallafa, sannan ta yi kira da a rufe shafukansa na sada zumunta "don hana ci gaba da yada kiyayya ga Yahudawa".
Wiley, wanda aka fi sani da Godfather of Grime kuma sunansa na ainihi Richard Cowie, ya samu lambar yabo ta MBE saboda hidimar da ya yi wa waka a 2018.
"Rashin nasara" a Amurka na kawo cikas ga binciken magungunan coronavirus
The duniya kokarin samar da amfani anti-Covid magunguna da ake hampered da Amurka saboda masu bincike suna gwajin kwayoyi a "m, willy-nilly hanya", da gwani manyan Birtaniya ta shirin ya yi gargadin.
Shirin gwajin farfadowa na Birtaniya, wanda ya hada da marasa lafiya 12,000 a asibitocin Birtaniya da dama, ya riga ya gano wani sabon magani mai ban sha'awa don magance cutar sannan kuma ya nuna wasu biyu - wadanda a baya ake tunanin za su iya ceton rai - a matsayin marasa amfani.
Amma gazawar tsarin kiwon lafiya na Amurka don daidaita wannan fitarwa yana nufin cewa har yanzu ba a kimanta wasu magunguna masu ban sha'awa waɗanda za a iya share su don amfani da su ba.
Musamman, plasma na convalescent (jini na jini wanda aka samo daga marasa lafiya na Covid-19 kuma wanda ke dauke da kwayoyin garkuwar jiki wanda zai iya kare wasu daga cutar) har yanzu ba a gwada shi yadda ya kamata ba a cikin gwaji mai yawa.
Farfesa Martin Landray, daya daga cikin wadanda suka kirkiri shirin na farfadowa, ya ce, "An riga an bai wa dubban mutane jini a Amurka, amma ba a yi amfani da su ba.
Landray, wani kwararre a fannin shirya gwaje-gwajen magunguna masu yawa, ya kara da cewa, "Suna bai wa mutane jini ne kawai da fatan zai yi aiki. An ba da adadi mai yawa kuma har yanzu ba su san ko yana taimakawa ko cutarwa ko kuma ba shi da wani tasiri ba".
Amurka ta gaza gudanar da gwaje-gwaje masu yawa, kuma hakan ya haifar da samar da magani mara kyau.
Gwaje-gwajen magunguna na bazuwar su ne ma'aunin zinariya don gano magunguna masu amfani.
Suna cire kuskuren da ba a sani ba wanda zai iya rufe hukuncin likitoci.
Dubban mutane suna ba da magani kuma dubban wasu suna ba da placebo.
Babu wanda ya san abin da aka ba su.
Sa'an nan sakamakon da aka kwatanta da kuma inganci na magani bayyana.
Ta wannan hanyar, Recovery ya iya nuna cewa steroid dexamethasone ya rage mutuwa da kashi uku cikin dari a cikin marasa lafiya na Covid-19 a kan ventilators.
Har ila yau, ya nuna cewa maganin hydroxychloroquine - da kuma hadewar magungunan lopinavir da ritonavir - ba su da tasiri wajen ceton rayukan marasa lafiya.
Muhimmanci wadannan gwaji da ake bukata sosai manyan lambobi na marasa lafiya da kuma babu guda asibiti yana da isasshen domin irin wannan bincike.
Birtaniya na da wata babbar fa'ida, wato tsarin kiwon lafiya na kasa da kasa.
Sabanin haka, aikin kiwon lafiyar Amurka ya rarrabu kuma nasarar da ta samu wajen nuna yiwuwar magani ita ce nuna amfani da maganin remdesivir mai tsada don hanzarta murmurewa daga wasu marasa lafiya na Covid-19.
"Akwai kuri'a da kuri'a na kananan kwayoyi gwaji shafe 'yan dozin ko' yan daruruwan marasa lafiya faruwa a Amurka amma babu wani abu na wani abu",Ya kara da Landray.
"Suna kasa yin manyan gwaje-gwaje, gwaje-gwaje na bazuwar kuma hakan ya kawo karshen samar da magani mara kyau.
Landray ya ce wannan gazawar ta zama abin takaici musamman idan aka yi la'akari da amfani da plasma na warkewa, wanda likitoci da dama ke ganin zai iya taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen kula da marasa lafiya masu fama da cutar Covid-19.
"Idan ka dubi Amurka, an yi amfani da adadi mai yawa na wannan magani ba tare da son rai ba. Birtaniya ta fi dacewa idan aka kwatanta da abin da ke faruwa a can, "in ji shi.
Farfesa Peter Horby, wani kwararre a kan cututtuka masu yaduwa kuma daya daga cikin wadanda suka kirkiri shirin farfadowa, ya ce: "Akwai rahotanni na marasa lafiya 20,000 da ke samun plasma a cikin wani rukuni amma babu daya daga cikin marasa lafiyar da aka yi wa rajista.
Idan sun sanya wadannan marasa lafiya cikin gwaje-gwaje na bazuwar, yanzu za mu sami amsa mai kyau game da tasirin plasma na convalescent. "
Horby ya kara da cewa yanzu haka kungiyar UK Recovery ta kaddamar da gwajin jinin wadanda suka warke, amma ba ta sa ran samun sakamakon gwajin sai nan da karshen wannan shekarar.
Masar ta fara rijistar bayanan masu jefa kuri'a a kasashen waje don zaben majalisar dattawa
Hukumar zabe ta kasa (NEA) a ranar Asabar ta fara rajistar bayanan masu kada kuri'a a cikin jirgin don fara jefa kuri'unsu a zaben majalisar dattawa da za a gudanar a ranar 9 da 10 ga watan Agusta, a cewar shafin yanar gizon hukumar ta NEA.
Dole ne masu jefa kuri'a su yi rajistar bayanan su da kuma ofishin jakadancin da ke da alaka da zama a kasashen waje a shafin yanar gizo na NEA daga ranar 25 zuwa 31 ga watan Yuli.
Hukumar ta NEA ta kuma wallafa wani bidiyo da ke bayanin matakan da masu kada kuri'a za su iya dauka don kada kuri'unsu ta hanyar imel, a matsayin wani bangare na matakan kariya daga annobar coronavirus.
Daga ranar 26 ga watan Yuli zuwa 8 ga watan Agusta ne wa'adin yakin neman zaben dan takarar majalisar dattawa zai kare, a cewar hukumar ta NEA.
Ministar kula da 'yan gudun hijira ta kasar Masar Nabila Makram ta yi kira ga 'yan kasar Masar da ke zaune a kasashen waje da su shiga zaben kamar yadda kundin tsarin mulkin kasar ya ba su dama.
Majalisar wakilan Masar a ranar 17 ga watan Yuni ta amince da dokar kafa majalisar dattawa, wadda za ta yi aiki a matsayin babbar majalisar dokokin kasar.
An amince da dokar da rinjayen kashi biyu cikin uku, yayin da 'yan majalisa hudu suka nuna rashin amincewarsu
Majalisar Dattijai za ta ƙunshi mambobi 300, 100 daga cikinsu an zaɓe su ta hanyar rufaffiyar jerin sunayen, 100 da aka zaɓa ta hanyar tsarin mutum, da kuma mambobi 100 da Shugaban Jamhuriyar ya nada
Wa'adin mambobin majalisar dattawa zai kasance shekaru biyar, daga ranar da aka fara taron majalisar na farko.
Za a zabi sabbin 'yan majalisar ne a cikin kwanaki sittin kafin cikar wa'adinsu.
Yayin da ake ci gaba da zanga-zanga, 'yan sanda na kokarin amfani da sabbin hanyoyin da ba su da illa
Yayin da ake ci gaba da tashe-tashen hankula tsakanin jami'an tsaro da masu zanga-zanga a Portland da kewayen kasar, ana ci gaba da muhawara kan yadda 'yan sanda za su rage amfani da karfin da ya wuce kima.
Wasu kamfanoni suna ci gaba da samar da sabbin kayan aiki na zamani kamar na'urar sarrafa hannu don 'yan sanda su yi amfani da su a maimakon zabin da ya fi hadari kamar barkonon tsohuwa, harsasai na roba da kuma gurneti.
Kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amnesty International ta yi nazari kan hotunan bidiyo 500 na zanga-zangar da aka yi daga ranar 26 ga watan Mayu zuwa 5 ga watan Yuni, inda ta gano cewa an yi amfani da karfi fiye da kima a wurare 125 a jihohi 40 da kuma gundumar Columbia.
"Mun ga yadda aka yi amfani da hayaki mai sa hawaye, barkonon tsohuwa, barkonon tsohuwa, harsasai masu karfin milimita 40, kusan dukkanin makaman da ba su da illa an yi amfani da su ta hanyoyin da ba su dace ba", in ji mai bincike kan makamai na kungiyar Amnesty International Brian Castner.
Duk da haka, wasu nace cewa da ciwon zažužžukan da muhimmanci ga guje wa bukatar a wuta.
Corey Pegues, tsohon mataimakin sifeton 'yan sanda na New York, ya ce: "Duk wadannan na'urori ya kamata su kasance a hannun 'yan sanda don amfani da su ba tare da amfani da makami mai linzami ba saboda sana'a ce kawai a Amurka inda 'yan kasa ke ba ka dama ka dauki ranka".
Daya daga cikin sababbin kayan aikin da ake kira Bola Wrap, na'urar hannu ce da ke harba igiyar Kevlar mai tsawon kafa 8 wadda ke zagaye da wanda ake zargi.
Akwai Long Range Acoustic na'urorin, kuma aka sani da sauti canons, directed makamashi makamai da amfani da lasers to zafi mutum ta fata, sabon projectiles sanya daga abubuwa kamar kumfa da kuma chalk, wari bama-bamai, kuma ba shakka da Taser.
Hannayen jari na Axon, kamfanin da ke kera Taser, ya karu da sama da kashi 18%, inda ya kai kololuwa a lokacin da zanga-zangar ta rikide zuwa tashin hankali kwanaki bayan kisan George Floyd da 'yan sanda suka yi.
Ana sa ran kasuwar makaman da ba su da illa za ta kai dala biliyan 11.85 nan da shekarar 2023.
Ku kalli bidiyon don kallon sabbin kayan aikin fasaha na zamani da 'yan sanda ke amfani da su don rage karfi, yadda ake tsara su, da kuma abin da ke cikin hadari ga makomar aikin 'yan sanda da al'ummomin da suke bauta wa.
Magajin garin Kansas City ya yi maraba da taimakon gwamnatin tarayya wajen warware kisan kai, amma ya damu game da muradun Trump
Magajin garin Kansas City Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi game da dalilan da suka sa Shugaba Trump ya tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya zuwa biranen Amurka - yana mai cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimakon wajen warware kashe-kashen da ke faruwa a birnin na tsakiyar yammacin Amurka, yana ganin matakin zai iya kasancewa game da bunkasa damar sake zaben Trump.
"Na yi matukar takaici a wannan makon [da] shugaban kasa ya ambaci zanga-zangar George Floyd, ya ambaci yunkurin Black Lives Matter", in ji Lucas, wani dan jam'iyyar Democrat, a kan "Fox News Sunday" game da zanga-zangar baya-bayan nan game da rashin daidaito tsakanin launin fata da kuma cin zarafin 'yan sanda.
"Wannan shi ne ba haka al'amarin a Kansas City. Mun yi shekara-shekara ƙaruwa [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kan shi ne a zahiri share wasu daga cikin unsolved kisan kai. "
Lucas kara da cewa: "Bari mu yi kokarin a pinpointed da niyya mayar da hankali a kan warware kisan kai ... Ina ganin idan ka saurari 'yan kalamai ... muna farin ciki da aiki tare da tarayya jamiái a cikin wani iyaka ikon yinsa. "
Duk da aniyarsa ta sa jami'an gwamnatin tarayya su yi aiki tare da jami'an tsaro na cikin gida, Lucas ya ce kalaman Trump - musamman dangane da takaddamar da ke tattare da dabarun da jami'an gwamnatin tarayya suka yi amfani da su a Portland, Oregon - ya sa da yawa daga cikin mazabarsa sun nuna damuwa game da kasancewar jami'ai a kan titunan birnin.
"Abin da ba mu bukatar shi ne mafi man fetur a kan wuta daga tarayya jamiái yi, ina ganin, wani m siyasa batun", in ji shi.
Trump a ranar Laraba ya sanar da cewa yana tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen yaki da karuwar wasu laifuka - wani mataki da ke nuna fadada tsoma bakin fadar White House a cikin dokokin gida yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin shugaban kasa na "doka da oda".
The "surge" na jamiái sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da kuma sauran Amurka birane ne wani ɓangare na Operation Legend - mai suna bayan 4-shekara LeGend Taliferro, wanda aka fatally harbe yayin da barci a Kansas City Apartment marigayi watan jiya.
Duk da yake aika jami'an gwamnatin tarayya don taimakawa jami'an tsaro na gida ba sabon abu ba ne - Babban Mai Shari'a Bill Barr ya sanar da irin wannan yunkuri a watan Disamba ga birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - irin jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da aka aika, da wasu daga cikin dabarun su, sun tayar da damuwa a tsakanin 'yan majalisun jihohi da na kananan hukumomi.
Yawancin 'yan majalisar dokoki daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana a kan gwamnatin Trump ta tura jami'an zuwa garuruwansu, musamman bayan rahotannin da ke cewa jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da ba a san ko su wanene ba sun tsare masu zanga-zanga a Portland kuma suka tafi da su cikin motocin da ba a san ko su wanene ba.
Portland ta fuskanci zanga-zanga kusan kullum kan cin zarafin 'yan sanda da wariyar launin fata tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd lokacin da yake tsare a hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
Hukumomi a yankin sun kuma yi korafin cewa karuwar tashe-tashen hankulan ne kawai ya kara rura wutar rikicin, kuma kwararru a fannin shari'a sun ce yunkurin ba shi da tushe saboda irin mawuyacin halin da Amurka ke ciki - tare da annoba, rashin aikin yi na tarihi da kuma yawan zarge-zarge kan wariyar launin fata da kuma yadda 'yan sanda ke kula da mutane masu launin fata.
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na AP ya caccaki sakatariyar yada labaran fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany kan yadda take gabatar da bayanai na siyasa - amma manema labarai na ci gaba da yi mata tambayoyi na siyasa - RT USA News
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya zargi sakatariyar yada labaran fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany da damun kafafen yada labarai ta hanyar mayar da rahotanninta na siyasa maimakon bayanai - da alama ta manta cewa manema labarai ne ke zabar tambayoyin.
Wata kasida da kamfanin dillancin labarai na AP, wanda shi ne kamfanin dillancin labarai mafi girma a Amurka, ya wallafa a ranar Asabar, ta ce taron manema labarai na fadar White House na iya zama "wata al'ada da aka karya", saboda McEnany ta mayar da shi "tallace-tallace mai inganci ga shugaban da ke fuskantar sake zabe, wurin da ake kai hare-hare kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma dandalin da ke da karancin bayanai" game da abin da gwamnati ke yi.
A karshe daga cikin wadanda da'awar ne indisputable, kamar yadda da wuya wani sabon bayani da aka saukar a cikin briefings.
Abin da kamfanin dillancin labarai na AP ya kasa ambata shi ne cewa da wuya a nemi wani sabon bayani a taron manema labarai.
'Yan jarida suna yawan amfani da manema labarai na Fadar White House don jawo hankalin kansu, wani nau'i na fasaha da Jim Acosta na CNN ya kammala.
Sun wuce dangantakar abokantaka ta kafofin watsa labarai da gwamnati, suna maimaita juna a cikin tambayar tambayoyin da aka yi da nufin kawai su zargi Shugaba Donald Trump.
A wasu lokuta, suna gabatar da kansu a matsayin labarai, kamar lokacin da wakiliyar CBS News Weijia Jiang ta mayar da martani ga "tambayar China" daga Trump ta hanyar yin nuni da wariyar launin fata: "Sir, me yasa kake fadin hakan musamman a gare ni?"
Wani taron manema labarai da aka yi a ranar 6 ga watan Yuli ya bayar da misali mai kyau na yadda taron ya daina zama wata kafa ta samun bayanai masu ma'ana ga Amurkawa.
A wani sako da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter a safiyar yau, Trump ya ce tashoshin talabijin na NASCAR sun fuskanci koma-baya sakamakon zargin da ake yi wa matukin motar Bubba Wallace da laifin nuna kiyayya da kuma matakin da hukumar ta dauka na haramta nuna tutar Kudancin Amurka a wuraren da ake gudanar da gasar.
Kamar yadda aka yi tsammani, yawancin tambayoyin sun kasance game da tweet a matsayin mai jarida bayan mai jarida ya tambayi McEnany tambayoyin da aka tsara don ya sa ta ce Trump yana goyon bayan tutar Confederate.
McEnany ba ta ba da amsar da manema labarai ke so ba - wani sauti da zai cutar da Trump - amma ta amsa sau da yawa ta ce shugaban bai dauki matsayi a kan tutar Confederate ba kuma jigon sakonsa shi ne cewa ana nuna magoya bayan NASCAR a matsayin masu wariyar launin fata.
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na AP ya ce ta yi "mamaki" a lokacin da aka yi mata bayani.
The AP ta labarin echoed a Washington Post m-ed shafi a farkon wannan watan da ABC News wakilin Jonathan Karl, wanda kuma shi ne shugaban White House Correspondents Association.
Karl ya ce, "tabbatar da gaskiya da kuma amfani da fadar White House don manufofin siyasa ne kawai ya saba wa amincewar jama'a".
Duk da haka McEnany ta sauri wit da combative style sun sanya ta gwarzo na wasu Trump magoya bayan, tun lokacin da ta ba ta farko bayani a kan May 1 bayan shan kan matsayin latsa sakataren a watan Afrilu.
Masu matsa lamba sun kasance ba a nan ba fiye da shekara guda kafin a nada ta.
Kamar sauran bangarori na harkokin siyasa a Washington, dangantakar mai magana da yawun fadar White House da kafafen yada labarai ta sauya matuka a zamanin Trump.
Wannan canji ya zo daga bangarorin biyu kuma ya riga ya zo kafin zuwan McEnany.
Soyayyar tsohuwar sakatariyar yada labarai Sarah Huckabee Sanders da mai barkwanci Michelle Wolf ta yi a liyafar cin abincin dare ta White House Correspondents a watan Afrilun 2018 ta yi muni sosai har ma mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen gidan talabijin na MSNBC Mika Brzezinski ya kira ta da "abin takaici".
Wakiliyar kamfanin dillancin labarai na AP a fadar White House Jill Colvin ta gaishe da McEnany a jawabinta na farko inda ta tambaye ta, "Shin za ka yi alkawarin ba za ka taba yi mana karya daga wannan dandalin ba?"
Fox News siyasa Analyst Brit Hume, a tsohon soja na fiye da 50 shekaru a aikin jarida wanda yana da wani 1989-1996 stint a matsayin ABC ta shugaba White House wakilin, ya ce manema labarai a yau nuna "m hali" a cikin briefing dakin saboda su raini ga trump.
Yana da saboda su anti-Trump mayar da hankali, ya ce wannan makon a kan Fox ta Tucker Carlson Tonight shirin, 'yan jarida suna sakaci da tattara manufofin labarai.
"Ba wai kawai wasa ba ne", in ji Hume game da manufar masu matsin lamba.
"Ba wai kawai wani yunkuri ne na kunyata wani jami'in gwamnati ba, abu ne na neman bayanai".
Safari shakatawa baboons gani dauke da makamai da wukake, screwdrivers da CHAINSAW kamar yadda 'pranksters ba su makamai don wargaza motoci'
An dade da sanin cewa birrai a gidan ajiye namun daji na Knowsley safari park da ke Merseyside, sukan yi kaca-kaca da duk wanda ya tsaya a cikin gidan ajiye namun dajin kuma su kwace wiper ko madubi.
A wurin shakatawa na Knowsley safari park da ke Merseyside, an samu birrai dauke da wukake da adduna har ma da bindigogi masu sarrafa kansu.
Ma'aikata na fargabar cewa 'yan damfara na bai wa birrai makamai, wadanda aka san su da kai hari kan duk wanda ya tsaya ya cire wipers da madubin mota.
Yanzu ma'aikata na fargabar cewa masu ziyara na amfani da makamai masu guba "don dariya" don karfafa hare-haren da suke kai wa, har ma an ga birrai suna wawason kayan aiki da kansu.
Wani ma'aikacin wurin shakatawar ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa: "Ba mu da tabbacin ko wasu daga cikin baƙi ne ke ba su makamai don su ga yadda suke kai wa motoci hari, ko kuma suna kama su ne daga cikin manyan motoci da motoci".
"Za su shiga akwatunan kayan aikin mutane su rika yawo da su, an ga daya daga cikin gwaggon birin yana yawo da wata na'ura mai sarrafa kanta".
Wani ma'aikacin wurin ya ce: "An gano birai dauke da wukake da adduna, ina mamakin ko wasu daga cikin baki ne ke ba su".
